{
  "element": {
    "sourceTag": "container",
    "type": "custom",
    "children": [
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "HOW TO PLAY"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "22",
          "fontweight": "bold",
          "color": "#8888ff"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-2"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "GOAL: Move all 52 cards to the four foundation piles, building each suit from Ace to King."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "11",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "100%"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-3"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "TABLEAU: 7 columns. Build down in alternating colors (red on black). Move groups of face-up cards between columns. Empty columns accept any King."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "11",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "100%"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-4"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "FOUNDATION: 4 piles (top area). Build up by suit from Ace to King."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "11",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "100%"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-5"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "STOCK: Click to draw cards. Draw 1 or Draw 3 depending on mode."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "11",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "100%"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-6"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "BROWSER CONTROLS"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "13",
          "color": "#00ffff",
          "paddingTop": "4"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-7"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Click card to select, click destination to move. Drag cards for direct placement. Right-click to auto-send to foundation. Double-click for auto-move. ESC=pause, Z=undo, Y=redo, H=hint, R=new game."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "11",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "100%"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-8"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Keyboard shortcuts: Press 1-8 on title to quick-start a mode."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "11",
          "color": "#aaaaaa",
          "width": "100%"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-9"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "VR CONTROLS"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "13",
          "color": "#00ffff",
          "paddingTop": "4"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-10"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Trigger=select/place card, A=undo, B=hint, Thumbstick=pause. Laser pointer for menus and card interaction."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "11",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "100%"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-11"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "FEATURES"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "13",
          "color": "#ff8800",
          "paddingTop": "4"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-12"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Auto-save every 10s. Resume from title screen if you close the browser."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "10",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "100%"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-13"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Undo/Redo: Full undo history with redo support. New moves clear redo."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "10",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "100%"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-14"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Efficiency grade: A+ to F rating based on moves and time."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "10",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "100%"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-15"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Win streak bonus: Consecutive wins earn escalating XP."
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "10",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "100%"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-16"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "MODES"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "13",
          "color": "#ffcc00",
          "paddingTop": "4"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-17"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
        "children": [
          "Klondike 1 / Klondike 3 / Timed (5m) / Vegas ($)"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "fontsize": "10",
          "color": "#cccccc",
          "width": "100%"
        },
        "dataUid": "uid-18"
      },
      {
        "sourceTag": "text",
        "type": "custom",
